WEBVTT

1
00:13:05.570 --> 00:13:07.040 
你干嘛  你要改吗
What are you doing? Are you correcting it?

2
00:13:07.060 --> 00:13:08.740 
所有格的  "的"
Apostrophe "S".

3
00:13:08.760 --> 00:13:11.800 
我们要和法西斯主义作斗争  不是标点符号
We're fighting against fascism, not punctuation.

4
00:13:11.820 --> 00:13:13.260 
带上帽子  穿上学士服
Wow. Dig the cap and gownship.

5
00:13:13.260 --> 00:13:14.480 
好像回到学校一样
I feel like I'm back in school, man.

6
00:13:14.480 --> 00:13:16.300 
你应该回炉重造
You should be back in school.

7
00:13:16.320 --> 00:13:18.820 
这文章看起来像一群豺狼写的
This looks like it was written by a pack of jackals.

8
00:13:18.820 --> 00:13:20.780 
听着亚伯  你变得有些讨人厌
You know what, Abe? You're becoming a bit of a drag.

9
00:13:20.780 --> 00:13:22.260 
讨厌  讨厌  讨厌鬼
Drag, drag, drag.

10
00:13:22.260 --> 00:13:24.040 
我们才完成首刊诶
We just finished our first paper.

11
00:13:24.080 --> 00:13:25.220 
对啊
That's right.

12
00:13:25.360 --> 00:13:28.080 
埃兹拉实现了自我突破
And Ezra has outdone himself.

13
00:13:30.000 --> 00:13:32.120 
我以为你是艾伦的女朋友
I thought you were Alan's girlfriend.

14
00:13:32.340 --> 00:13:34.640 
女人不是任何男人的所有物
No woman is any man's property.

15
00:13:34.640 --> 00:13:35.920 
你应该关注内容
You should be looking at the ideas.

16
00:13:35.920 --> 00:13:37.520 
不是拼写和语法
Not the spelling. Not the grammar.

